{"tid":1637752,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"換美元啦，手快有手慢冇","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T23:25:50.000Z","uid":50801,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"c888db89c46bd2e241d7556d5a55f6d0069b6214","tid":1637752,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"兌換美元常見問題<br />\n<br />\nQ1. 我係咪要兌換美元? / 我有冇需要兌換美元?<br />\nA1. 全屬閣下個人決定，視乎你對港元有幾大信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ2. 我應該兌換幾多%資產? / 我係學生，有冇需要兌換？<br />\nA2. 都係果句，全屬閣下個人決定<br />\n因為每個人既資產管理差天共地，所以俾唔到正確答案你<br />\n我自己就定左條線，不妨當做例子參考：只保留兩個月左右生活開支既港元，其餘兌晒做美元，反正只要唔爆，邊日我都可以兌返做港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ3. 我唔想兌美元，可否改兌其他外幣/人民幣(下略為RMB) ?<br />\nA3. 又講多次，全屬閣下個人決定<br />\n不過港元冇同其他貨幣掛鈎，投資涉及風險，兌換價格可升可跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸問題<br />\nQ3.1 但係XX幣呢排升緊喎?<br />\nA3.1 呢個已經係投資問題，並不在本post討論範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ4. 我想知邊度有得兌換美元 ?<br />\n正常途徑︰銀行 或 找換店<br />\n銀行<br />\n優：保證真鈔(?)，可直接存入外幣戶口<br />\n劣：兌換價通常相對較差，兌換/提取超過USD$1500多數要預約<br />\n找換店<br />\n優：兌換價較靚，HKD$80000內交易通常不用預約(頭盔：請自行向找換店查詢)<br />\n劣：微型找換店有機會中伏(假鈔) 因應洗黑錢條例，HKD$80000以上交易需登記身份證<br />\n兩者優劣之處有更多討論空間，需要更多資料比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸問題<br />\nQ4.1 咁有咩找換店推介，間鋪響邊，點解揀呢間?<br />\nA4.1 分幾個大區講啦<br />\n港島區：百年找換<br />\n九龍及新界：發達鳥 <br />\n離島︰出返市區啦，住咁偏就係咩都冇嫁啦<br />\n大嶼山︰機埸找換店個價太差，所以唔推薦，出市區啦<br />\n店舖地址請自行google，至於點解揀呢兩間，因為多人用，死都有大把人陪葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ5. 我兌完可以放邊?<br />\nA5. 量多可到銀行開立離岸戶口，量少就放餅罐啦<br />\n我自己都係放餅罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸問題<br />\nQ5.1 離岸戶口點開? / 點防家賊? <br />\nA5.1 開立離岸戶口涉及大量步驟，請google或問巴打<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1335920/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1335920/</a>，呢條link係前人既教學，不妨參考<br />\n至於防家賊既野，就自己搞惦佢啦，不論係保安方法定係個家賊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ5.2 咁我放本地外幣戶口唔得咩？<br />\nA5.2 假如，我強調假如，本地銀行系統停擺，邊度有錢俾你攞到出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ6. 我兌黎兌去咪蝕差價同手續費囉？<br />\nA6. 以匯率維持現狀計算，指( USD $1 : HKD $7.75~7.85 )<br />\n理論值︰7.85買入 &gt; 7.75賣出，每百港元輸1.3，約1.3%，但應該冇咩奇才可以去到咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ7. 我應該邊日去換，要唔要等個價靚先兌？<br />\nA7. 時機既野自己判斷，不過崩盤可以係幾日就完成，驚到時你想兌都冇人收<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ8. 仆你個街，係咁叫人換換換，搞亂金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母，用下個豬腦啦，中國邊有咁易死，話晒全球第二大經濟體系<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聯繫匯率行左幾十年啦，唔會出事架戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA8. 假如閣下覺得港元根基穩健，唔洗理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如閣下睇好RMB前景，歡迎大手買入，all in RMB，「In China, We Trust」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畢竟你既錢其實唔關我事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴打討論, 補充同修改<br />\n我相信集體智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個Q &amp; A，已經有一個月咁耐，資料有機會過時，請見諒"},{"pid":"4d927524dcd297cd0e23c0a0d6e531ed937e05ab","tid":1637752,"uid":36089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"巴打又係你，推"},{"pid":"c8fcd15f42e708558b848ed0b9a9aca588da2113","tid":1637752,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">消費日</span></span></strong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f252073c6febc1043606cb11ebb201e29d7b130a","tid":1637752,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df01b7451fbb2172a5d4f2376acab569f1cf089b","tid":1637752,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"港紙遲早變廢紙"},{"pid":"c459e4d55d46c074c040da6f2a8dd34bcd4c5095","tid":1637752,"uid":188484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"推，好啲嘅資產管理應該持有不同國家嘅資產，唔好揸死一個國家，可以減低風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac225a05b607c461dde2a468ad5a8ffbb57c5b30","tid":1637752,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ac9638d578b68c76dffe68ac4822552a23dfc3","tid":1637752,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:29:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"941114eaf045f2618cebd9cd496a236ad7d11787","tid":1637752,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac225a05b607c461dde2a468ad5a8ffb